Do great melee damage to 1 random enemy. 
Frost Ball  
Do frost damage to 1 random enmy and chance to put back the target on the turn bar.
Fire Ball
Do fire damage and chance to burn the target.
Heal
Heal the friendly unit with lowest health heavily.
Double Shot
Do great ranged damage to 2 random enemies. 
Arrow Rain
Do great melee damage to enemies in back row. 
Cleave
Do great melee damage to enemies in front row. 
Fire Rain
Do great fire damage to enemies in front row. 
Frost Breath
Do great frost damage to all enemies. 
Frost Arrows
Do great frost damage to 3 random enemies. 
Cure
Heal 3 friendly units with lowest health moderately.
Fire Breath
Do great fire damage to all enemies. 
Song of Life
